sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as "AI Platform"
    participant Extract as "getAuthToken(req)<br/>at server.js:502-515"
    participant MCPBridge as "MCP Bridge"
    participant AutoMem as "AutoMem API"
    
    Note over Client,AutoMem: Authentication Token Extraction
    Client->>Extract: Request with auth
    
    alt Authorization: Bearer token
        Extract->>Extract: Parse Bearer token
        Extract-->>MCPBridge: token (preferred)
    else X-API-Key header
        Extract->>Extract: Read X-API-Key
        Extract-->>MCPBridge: token
    else X-API-Token header
        Extract->>Extract: Read X-API-Token
        Extract-->>MCPBridge: token
    else Query parameter
        Extract->>Extract: Read ?api_key or ?apiKey or ?api_token
        Extract-->>MCPBridge: token
    end
    
    Note over Client,AutoMem: AutoMem API Request
    MCPBridge->>AutoMem: POST /memory<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}
    
    alt Valid token
        AutoMem-->>MCPBridge: 201 Created
        MCPBridge-->>Client: JSON-RPC success
    else Invalid token
        AutoMem-->>MCPBridge: 401 Unauthorized
        MCPBridge-->>Client: JSON-RPC error
    end